tomboy: tomboy (GNOME Simple Note Taking)
tomboy:
tomboy: Tomboy is a desktop note-taking application for Linux and Unix. Simple 
tomboy: and easy to use, but with potential to help you organize the ideas and 
tomboy: information you deal with every day. Tomboy is written in C# and 
tomboy: utilizes the Mono runtime and Gtk#. Automatic spell-checking is 
tomboy: provided by GtkSpell.
